Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:15.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.58,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who agreed to take this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.14,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:30.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who begged you to let me fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.22,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost done, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:42.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to finish the job, thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.64,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fight some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We start heading back to \Nthe capital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.61,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're wrapping up the trading trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your treatment takes priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:05.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We need potent holy water from the \Ncapital's church to dispel that curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:08.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have a long road ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:09.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:10.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:16.21,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:18.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:19.36,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.26,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.23,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,something's going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,a human child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.31,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,OP Card,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:20.13,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}Melty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.80,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Those birds looked yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.31,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,If we go after them now, \Nwe can hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those were your own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.31,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,My own kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.40,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,So big...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.61,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a filolial?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.32,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.13,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:47.90,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.79,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I've always dreamed of \Ntalking with a filolial!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.30,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,For you. It's dried meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.94,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.38,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be from the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, she's too well dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably a noble's \Ndaughter or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.16,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.40,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.14,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.36,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.32,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.00,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.09,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.64,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.46,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She must love filolials a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We still have work to do in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, you can \Nplay with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.70,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.98,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.10,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.78,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.54,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You can transform, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.48,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.07,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She took that surprisingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They both seem to like their new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo needs to spend time with\Nother kids, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:15.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, can I play some more with Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just be back by sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.33,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.57,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Our Savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.20,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Help her too, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to say that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.62,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.43,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I made a friend today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That Mel girl from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:15.44,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:19.21,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's traveled to a \Nlot of places, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:24.74,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And she told me so many \Nthings I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:32.01,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,And she says she got separated from her \Npeople when she was playing with filolials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? Separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.73,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for showing up so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:48.04,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Could you let me accompany \Nyou for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.88,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way to the royal capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:59.44,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,but, uh, when I saw the filolials...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:04.93,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I was so engrossed in playing with them, \NI got separated from my guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.50,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're leaving for the \Ncapital tomorrow, Savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.41,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.36,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did she learn about me from the villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.45,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that I'm making a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.57,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,But please, I must return to the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.83,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.64,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If she is a noble's daughter, \Nwe might get a reward,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:33.16,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,but it might also cause problems if \NI'm the one who takes her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.58,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I want you to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:43.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We can't turn her down when \Nshe's having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to cough up a reward, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.17,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I shall ask my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.77,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.12,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.79,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We truly can't find the words to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have money than words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I'm here,\NI'll collect everything I'm owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.95,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:37.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can keep watch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You can sleep for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.63,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They're both so quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny after how much noise \Nthey were making earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.14,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have you catching a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Mel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But Filo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:26.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she did say \Nher own kind looked yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.05,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We saw nothing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If we just destroy the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:43.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What, you want us to go confess that \NFilo ate some noble's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:49.49,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, where's Mel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.20,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.30,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping in my feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.83,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Mel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.94,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:11.13,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan's feathers are \Nso soft and comfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So you took off your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.60,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:23.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do these feathers have \Nsleep-inducing powers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.60,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.53,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.74,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you collect the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.82,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.59,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.14,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We'll miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.80,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why's the shield the only one missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.27,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.48,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.23,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness the Pope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.11,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.31,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.91,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your magnificent \Nduel at the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:04.15,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,The way you fought with the odds stacked \Nagainst you left a deep impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.70,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I could not believe you held your \Nown despite wielding only a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I need the most potent holy water \Nyou have to dispel a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.64,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Holy water, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.75,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Then please make your offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:24.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:28.01,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the most potent one,\N that'll be one gold coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's too expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:37.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to you, a gold coin means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.59,sign_23102_195_Cheap_Holy_Water,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(401,1)}Cheap Holy Water (Crude)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted a gold coin for {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.39,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring a low-quality item?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.93,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.92,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,God is equally compassionate to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:02.00,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,If you did this to satisfy \Nyour personal beliefs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.14,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,then I hope you repent at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.28,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.33,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my fellow disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I won't complain as long \Nas I get my money's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.30,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful for your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:21.17,sign_23102_195_Cheap_Holy_Water,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(397,147)}Curse-Dispelling Holy Water (Pure)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.25,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,God shows us all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.85,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Please be grateful for his guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.39,main,Pope,0000,0000,0000,,Everything we have, we are \Ngiven by God's grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about patronizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.31,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.21,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why are we running?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do? He's coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.04,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:10.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:14.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably after me, so let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:15.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:17.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go get Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll regroup by the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.10,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Surely... I lost him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.44,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You attacked me in the middle of the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.79,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.53,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that slave girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.54,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Free her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:56.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real pest, too. Raphtalia is—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.19,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Not Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.69,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the blonde \Ngirl with wings on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.63,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her with you, so don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.25,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.70,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,So that's her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.76,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a girl as perfect as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.65,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's a girl who's \Njust like Freon-chan from {\i1}Hellworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.88,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to have a thing for angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:30.89,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,My heart has been in overdrive \Never since my first look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.34,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I love other worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.42,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I love blonde angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, what's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.90,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.89,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,That fat bird's yours too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.90,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you and that chubster to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.27,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.43,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.93,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.58,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.93,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.88,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.19,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.44,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.57,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Spear Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the guy from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.81,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a public place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.40,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's no place for a personal duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.91,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,It is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.14,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Surround them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.41,main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.04,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:02.95,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I declare this an official duel between \Nthe Spear Hero and the Shield Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.93,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,with the authority vested \Nin me by the crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.00,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Put your weapons away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.99,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow the heroes to \Nfight among themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:25.82,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.63,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It's been far too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.30,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:38.06,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't think your or the hero's\N privilege can cover up this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.75,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.16,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.38,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Who would call a man that puts \Nlives at risk a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:54.17,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, your fun and \Ngames have gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.86,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply doing my job as the hero's aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:02.36,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Is making him fight in a public \Nplace your idea of aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.20,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,You dare defy me, your older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.91,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,If need be, I will let \NMother know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.42,top,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.35,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Melty is Myne's little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.29,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she's this country's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Motoyasu once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.86,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.34,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,That's your name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.18,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.00,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.56,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi's working you \Nlike a horse, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.04,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I like drawing the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.28,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, you swine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.84,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You're making her pull your \Nwagon like that fat bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.12,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.57,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You called me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.43,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You made fun of me the last time we met, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.67,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I did? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.26,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, spear guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.76,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-You were that fat bi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:18.07,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:22.25,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody take him to a doctor at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.35,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Filo wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. I'm proud of you, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:31.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,He always puts us through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,He had that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:38.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what's with that satisfied smirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.81,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Our Savior of the Heavenly Fowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.60,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.96,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:54.15,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, could you explain this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let us discuss things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.84,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.64,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You know that's not gonna fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We couldn't think \Nof a better place nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.28,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So? Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.35,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my late introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:14.22,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I am first in line to the throne of Melromarc,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:17.71,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Second Princess Melty Melromarc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.07,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thr...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,In line to the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:24.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be the next ruler, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're ahead of your older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:33.15,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My sister has always been a \Nproblem child due to her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:38.01,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:41.80,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,But this might be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.21,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.32,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:53.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.93,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}In the Midst of Turmoil
